{
  "id": "RAW_b5e7fa4a",
  "title": "国产 Claude Cowork 来了！支持 Skills、MCP 和专家 Agents，免费体验！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTU5OTQ1Nw==&mid=2653724226&idx=1&sn=78bd0d18ecbb62b27ccd2b8d8aa6b4a0",
  "date": "2026-01-23 12:02:00",
  "author": " (沃垠AI)",
  "siteName": "沃垠AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大家好，我是最近在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">钻研Work Automation</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的冷逸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上一篇写的Claude Code入门指南，已经5.7w+阅读量了，转发更是接近1w（不会都是发给自己的文件助手吧<img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 20px;vertical-align: middle;background-size: cover;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7478ac68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FYellowdog.png\">）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqra80czpt\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.20764119601328904\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"602\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240547\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f61bf54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPww9U6VoT1quic5Fp9QExQFAsyZ8TunLj1ErLj1gtMfRRFszXlGC6jkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上周末，又去北京参加了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">ACDC开发者大会</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，在圆桌环节分享了自己对Skills的理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqraeiepqn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240548\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8058b92d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPzaFX1d3fgicqYkIqAQG3zPjUy3ffFuKErESLhibBpasRrALRcEicfqUvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">能明显感觉到，大家都在疯狂学习Work Automation（自动化办公）。最近，海内外AI公司先后上线了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Claude Cowork、扣子2.0、Grok、阶跃AI桌面伙伴</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">等产品，专门针对自动化办公场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在这几天，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">MiniMax Agent</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也推出了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">桌面端</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（MiniMax的Cowork）和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Expert Agents</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（MiniMax的Skills）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有必要给大家深度体验一下，做个评测汇报。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506236477\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2b71a2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvic8DcjbZP6CtUD7nHjdLA0fB0eibP1sbkJBqTVafECcdFc416I0ia2VHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">一手体验</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">1）MiniMax Agent桌面端体验</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，MiniMax Agent桌面端已</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">支持macOS和Windows双端体验</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，直接前往</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">agent.minimaxi.com</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下载即可。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqrcud91fjg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4981481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240552\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e639e416&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPDeias4zG8bjxiczIpvxfzL08aoZbk4pNtKzhGibCFEicYmqQILQW3YZU9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下载安装好后，你会看到这样的用户指引。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqrd43fnhn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240549\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2532ad3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPWTABZ8I5jCvvtiap6qP3XCBhLH7qEoYR48hRdc0g5VcicRMojKNKkanA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">先简单认识一下它的界面。初看你会觉得，这好像和MiniMax Agent网页版没什么区别？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqrde4dyu3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240550\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c569701&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPYeyD0A4rYQR7WuvUUewqaMlgh1nlqrYZZf7IqnpAtm9RxEicwB17A3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但细看会发现，它多了一个指定工作区。可以选定一个工作目录，让AI来读取、分析和批量处理这个工作目录下的所有文件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个工作目录，其实就是MiniMax Agent工作的上下文。建议大家自行在“</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">头像-设置-通用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">”中选一个你觉得安全的文件夹位置，作为MiniMax Agent的启动目录。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们先来试一个简单的任务，比如我写文章会经常做的一件事——图片裁剪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一张图片，我可以自己用PS裁，那几十上百张呢？我们丢给MiniMax Agent试一下，输入任务要求：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">图片裁剪：将xx文件夹中的图片统一裁剪为1670 x 2970，并保存到 Output 子文件夹中。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqrdjsmq3f\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39285714285714285\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"868\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240551\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0ac027f4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPefibicWq1Swyq8w0hibdHU0tb2JXnSNj48NS8O3yL95kkA7NQho0YWITQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我看到结果的那一刻惊呆了，它总共就花了0.15s，不是几分钟也不是几秒钟，而是0.15秒啊，卧槽Σ(°ロ°)</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqrdqamonx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4943502824858757\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"708\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240553\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ba981588&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPHXUWIia0b6TvqycWo0ia2jiaWgMzR0ib5iaVdl3JU6rF6gM46oVrtD3W8pA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后的结果，它自己验收了一遍，我也检查了一遍，完全是我要的9:16尺寸（对应分辨率1670 x 2970）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">全过程我录了个屏，一帧未剪，也未做任何加速。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，我们再给它加点难度，帮我爬一下B站的评论，并分析内容要素。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">B站博主分析：访问“Unitree宇树科技”的Bilibili主页，并打开最新5期视频。抓取每个视频前 20 条高赞评论，分析观众情感，找出最打动观众的 3 个要素。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">宇树科技网址：<a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/521974986\" target=\"_blank\">https://space.bilibili.com/521974986</a></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MiniMax Agent有一个浏览器专家，这个时候派上了用场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqrdwx31oyr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.582909460834181\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"983\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240558\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=216b7137&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPrsYuNTFgtniab26HXfFfWBFquv3opq7P4s2qFjJIXeS5pJ9ibvoMjaCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">输入任务要求后，它就自己调用浏览器开始工作了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqre2br13ly\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7229166666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506240559\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b009c3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLP07VPMN0ib2zHHABM0Jqy3hibyXfyh6icsj8vKPKwiblF0MTw91yjHocU7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一切都在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">MiniMax Agent桌面端的后台</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">进行，不影响其他工作，我们可以继续在浏览器里干其他事情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">只需要等一会儿时间，这个任务结果就出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkqre7iz1zco\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.921544209215442\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"803\" style=\"box-shadow:rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color:transparent;border-radius:6px;width:561px;height:1078px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/NX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLP8lb0VrS07Bz2YaYTTr9Ficzojz09OcV1ZvbsswqzVib57ibOtlMibmYkGg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"803\" data-cropy2=\"1543.019607843137\" data-imgfileid=\"506240560\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ad76fcdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibC8iaLXFia3IYQPTMv4PqMSicLPHic7xKOssJNr2Pia0NHIbdjmPmrjkZEYs5CBzxXyLCBeiaKt4F5mWJSLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这分析还挺靠谱的，我感觉让我自己去统计，没有2-3个小时完全搞不定。而现在，直接丢给MiniMax Agent就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且，我注意到它采用的是端云协同的方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">怎么理解呢，就是这个Agent工作的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">所有数据都是存在你的本地，不会存在云端</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。而该上网的服务，它都能正常访问。这个就是，端云协同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" dat